    "name": "Amazon Neptune Neptune SPARQL API",
    "description": "W3C SPARQL 1.1 query language API for querying RDF graphs in Neptune. It provides an HTTP REST endpoint compatible with the SPARQL 1.1 protocol specification. Supports SELECT, ASK, CONSTRUCT, DESCRIBE query forms and INSERT/DELETE update operations. Uses HTTP/1.1 with HTTPS only.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Amazon Web Services",
